I tried your example, it doesn't load exr if I don't enable `exr` feature
`bevy = { version = "0.13.2" }`
But if enable it, example doesn't print any error
`bevy = { version = "0.13.2", features = ["exr"] }`
@cshenton-work That because this feature affects loader initialization [here](https://github.com/bevyengine/bevy/blob/60afec2a00da51dd2120351ca9a9df1744413d1e/crates/bevy_render/src/texture/mod.rs#L77)
